name: Skull painting on canvas
description:
Original skull design on canvas by DIABOLICAL ROBOT ART.. This vibrant, bright and funky painting on high quality Mont Marte canvas was created using Posca paint pens and sprayed with a matte lacquer to enhance the colors and preserve the painting.
The thick square canvas is 10x10 cm and is 4cm deep. 

The canvas comes with a free art pack of stickers x5 stickers

Thanks for taking an interest in my art, If you would like to know more please search DIABOLICAL ROBOT ART on Facebook

name: 'Adventures in spay paint'
description:
'Adventures in spay paint'  an acrylic work on a used spray paint can, is a work inspired by the cartoon Adventure Time and painted by DIABOLICAL ROBOT.   This bright, vibrant and quirky painting was painted using posca paint pens and sealed with a matte lacquer to preserve the paint on the can.
The large sized can is 18cm high and 18 cm around. 

This artwork comes with a free 10 pack of art stickers 

Thanks for taking an interest in my art, if you would like to know more please search DIABOLICAL ROBOT ART on Facebook

name: STICKERS PACK OF 20- MIX OF HAND DRAWN AND PRINTED STICKERS
description:
Mixed sticker pack 20 printed stickers and 5 extra hand drawn stickers, 25 stickers total!!!!
All stickers are original designs on high quality thermal paper that are long lasting and stick to just about anything
The printed stickers will come from the range shown in the picture but hand drawn stickers will be different every time.
*note stickers are not suitable for outdoor use*
